properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 2:32PM EST until January 9 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt expected
along with seas up to 5 feet.

* WHERE...Portions of Gulf of Mexico.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 1 PM EST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 1 PM EST THURSDAY
